HEADWORD: Cater
<hw>Ca"ter</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[F. <ets>quatre</ets> four.]</ety>
<def>The four of cards or dice.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Cater</ent>⟦br⟧

